    "question_id" : 2401489,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In Spring 4.2+ you can now simply do:</p>\n\n<pre><code>@Component\nclass StartupHousekeeper {\n\n    @EventListener(ContextRefreshedEvent.class)\n    public void contextRefreshedEvent() {\n        //do whatever\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
