  "title" : "Execute method on startup in Spring",
  "body" : "<p>Is there any Spring 3 feature to execute some methods when the application starts for the first time? I know that I can do the trick of setting a method with <code>@Scheduled</code> annotation and it executes just after the startup, but then it will execute periodically.</p>\n"
